  "text": "The experimental manipulation of largescale chromatin structure [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] can provide a tool to determine the key cellular pathways and factors involved in genome-wide chromatin modifications. Analysis of the functional differentiation of chromatin structure in the oocyte genome in fact have wide-ranging implications for understanding the role of nuclear organization in meiosis, the events of nuclear reprogramming and the spatio-temporal regulation of gene expression during development and differentiation.",
